/*  Yammer - groups icons
    Version 3.05
    by gerdami
    CC BY-SA - Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike
    
    How to add icons to the right of groups in left column
    1. Go to the group
    2. Right click on the group logo
    3. Copy image location
    4. Paste it here but change icon size from 128x128 to 20x20
    5. Copy the sample span[title="All Company group"] together with the curved brackets
    6. Replace "All Company" by the group name
    7. Replace the url with the one create at point 4.
    8. Test with Preview
    9. Repeat with other groups
    10. Done
*/

